---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <!-- Hero2 Widget ******************* -->

  <Hero2
    tagline="Hourly Care or 24-Hour Care"
    title="Customized, Flexible Family and Client-Directed Care"
    subtitle="RIGHT ACCORD Private Duty-Home Health Care is a senior care provider and helps at home who cares about you. We can provide you or your family with senior helpers whether the need is short-term or long-term care for your loved one. You are in control. We work together to plan and design the care. Each client and family has unique needs and wants."
    actions={[
      {
        variant: 'primary',
        text: 'Schedule Appointment',
        href: 'https://forms.rightaccordhealthcare.com/schedule',
        icon: 'tabler:calendar-heart',
        target: '_blank',
      },
      { text: 'Contact Us', href: '/contact', target: '_blank' },
    ]}
    image={{
      src: HeroImage,
      alt: 'Hourly Care or 24-Hour Care',
    }}
  />

  <!-- Features Widget *************** -->

  <div
    id="learn-more"
    class="max-w-7xl mx-auto text-xl gap-5 leading-relaxed mb-10 p-5 flex flex-col mt-10 scroll-m-24"
  >
    <p>
      Sometimes the need is minimal and sometimes more care is necessary. At RIGHT ACCORD, we customize your care based
      on your needs. Hiring a caregiver from RIGHT ACCORD means you are in control and you are carefully matched to the
      right caregiver that best suit your needs. Caregivers are available from as little as 6 hours to 24 hours. There
      are no limits to the number of visits you can have per week or month. We will assist you in customizing schedule
      that will best benefit you and your loved one.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-semibold text-2xl mt-10 bg-main-blue text-white w-fit p-3">Hourly or 24 hour care benefits</h2>

    <p>
      While there are profound rewards for caregiving, family members are exposed to a wide array of stressors. RIGHT
      ACCORD offers a wide variety of senior services and options to make staying at home safe and possible offering
      benefits such as:
    </p>
    <ItemGrid
      items={benefits}
      columns={2}
      defaultIcon="tabler:check"
      classes={{
        container: 'gap-y-1 md:gap-y-1',
        panel: 'max-w-none',
        title: 'lg:text-base font-normal dark:text-slate-400 leading-6 ml-2 rtl:ml-0 rtl:mr-2',
        description: '',
        icon: 'flex h-4 w-4 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-green-600 dark:bg-green-700 text-gray-50 p-1 mt-1',
        action: 'text-lg font-medium leading-6 dark:text-white ml-2 rtl:ml-0 rtl:mr-2',
      }}
    />
  </div>

  <!-- Content Widget **************** -->

  <Content
    title="Services provided by an hourly or 24 hour in-home caregiver"
    isReversed
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Alzheimer’s / Dementia Care',
      },
      {
        title: 'Parkinson’s Disease Care',
      },
      {
        title: 'Post Stroke and other Neurological Care',
      },
      {
        title: 'COPD Care (Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease)',
      },
      {
        title: 'Care for Chronic Conditions such as Congestive Heart Failure, Diabetes, Arthritis',
      },
      {
        title: 'Hospice or End of Life Care',
      },
      {
        title: 'Facility or Hospital Sitter or Companion',
      },
    ]}
    image={{
      src: ServicesImage,
      alt: 'Hourly Care or 24-Hour Care',
    }}
  >
    <Fragment slot="content">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight dark:text-white sm:text-3xl mb-2">Our Specialty Care Areas:</h3>
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="bg">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-transparent"></div>
    </Fragment>
  </Content>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto text-xl gap-5 leading-relaxed mb-10 p-5 flex flex-col mt-10 scroll-m-24">
    <h2 class="font-semibold text-2xl mt-10 bg-main-blue text-white w-fit p-3">
      Assistance with personal care (hands-on care)
    </h2>

    <ItemGrid
      items={personalCare}
      columns={2}
      defaultIcon="tabler:check"
      classes={{
        container: 'gap-y-1 md:gap-y-1',
        panel: 'max-w-none',
        title: 'lg:text-base font-normal dark:text-slate-400 leading-6 ml-2 rtl:ml-0 rtl:mr-2',
        description: '',
        icon: 'flex h-4 w-4 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-green-600 dark:bg-green-700 text-gray-50 p-1 mt-1',
        action: 'text-lg font-medium leading-6 dark:text-white ml-2 rtl:ml-0 rtl:mr-2',
      }}
    />
    <h2 class="font-semibold text-2xl mt-10 bg-main-blue text-white w-fit p-3">Companionship and homemaking</h2>

    <ItemGrid
      items={companionship}
      columns={2}
      defaultIcon="tabler:check"
      classes={{
        container: 'gap-y-1 md:gap-y-1',
        panel: 'max-w-none',
        title: 'lg:text-base font-normal dark:text-slate-400 leading-6 ml-2 rtl:ml-0 rtl:mr-2',
        description: '',
        icon: 'flex h-4 w-4 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-green-600 dark:bg-green-700 text-gray-50 p-1 mt-1',
        action: 'text-lg font-medium leading-6 dark:text-white ml-2 rtl:ml-0 rtl:mr-2',
      }}
    />

    <p>
      If hourly in-home care by a caring, compatible and compassionate personal caregiver or home health care aide is
      right for you, please call us to schedule a free in-home assessment or to arrange care right away. Our A-Team of
      Caregivers ensures your 100% satisfaction. RIGHT ACCORD is here to provide you and your family with the comforts
      and peace of mind you deserve.
    </p>
  </div>

  <a href="https://forms.rightaccordhealthcare.com/book-download" target="_blank">
    <CallToAction
      bg="<div class='absolute inset-0 bg-blue-100'></div>"
      id="download"
      title="Download our booklet now!"
      subtitle="Get to know more about our services and how we can help you and your loved ones."
    >
      <div slot="actions" class="flex max-w-sm gap-4">
        <Button variant="link" target="_blank" href="https://forms.rightaccordhealthcare.com/book-download">
          <Image src={Booklet} alt="Survival Guide For Parent Care Image" width={400} />
        </Button>
      </div>
    </CallToAction>
  </a>
</Layout>
